summary:
- **All resolutions (1-13) passed at the General Meeting**, including:  
  - Ratification of share placements under Listing Rules 7.1 and 7.1A  
  - Approval for director participation in placements (Resolutions 4-7)  
  - Creation of performance shares (Resolution 8)  
  - Approval of TEPA Project acquisition (Resolution 9)  
  - Grant of performance rights to directors (Resolutions 10-13)  

No material trading or capital markets impact identified beyond standard governance approvals. Results were overwhelmingly in favor (94-96% FOR votes across key resolutions).
